def outliers(df, threshold, columns):
    for col in columns: 
        mask = df[col] > float(threshold)*df[col].std()+df[col].mean()
        df.loc[mask == True,col] = np.nan
        mean_property = df.loc[:,col].mean()
        df.loc[mask == True,col] = mean_property
    return df
